{"tid":467703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭醉酒休班女警襲擊後索償 女侍應終找到被告住址可派票","createTime":"2017-11-13T17:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T02:16:08.000Z","uid":43189,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ef85e4283a886794d38a47107215eaf275c6b2bc","tid":467703,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:25:59.000Z","msg":"休班女警醉酒後在街頭襲擊兩名不相識的女侍應，早前被裁定罪成及判社會服務令。其中日夜兼兩職的女侍應因被襲擊致腰椎受傷，未能上班兩個月，早前入稟小額錢債審裁處向女警追討3.2萬元。惟由於女警事後已辭職，警方拒絕透露女警聯絡地址，女侍應未能將法庭文件送達被告。案件今再訊，女侍應指透過民主黨立法會議員林卓廷取得被告地址，案件押後至下月6日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n申索人陳啟英，被告是袁樂欣，陳原於申索書被告地址一欄內填上灣仔軍器廠街警察總部，她得到被告地址後更改有關資料。<br />\n陳早前稱原本日打兩份工，日間做酒店服務員，晚間到酒樓當兼職侍應，去年7月8日凌晨下班後，她與同事行經天平邨時遭被告襲擊受傷，未完全康復。<br />\n<br />\n加入警隊7年的被告袁樂欣(26歲)在被裁定罪成後，曾向感化主任透露對事件感到後悔，願承擔後果並向事主賠償。<br />\n<br />\n案中另一名受傷女侍應黎孝芬早前亦曾入稟向被告追討賠償，亦因沒有被告的地址而案件被押後。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171113/57452623\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57452623&d=4YZ4Yc6MFKezhAiTN64FIDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=7441c032\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57452623&h=ef46f430\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171113/57452623</a>"},{"pid":"657801074d62d836dadf7e8a00acae50f71c340c","tid":467703,"uid":39064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:32:59.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"974fa11c114f768175a9689d6dd5e0412d0aafc0","tid":467703,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"aa57e8c25a810440b7b01328e4317c71b41d6ce4","tid":467703,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:39:37.000Z","msg":"感到後悔願承擔後果並向事主賠償條毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90c035eb6416a4eefa2e1c7e2cee92d5672c6ec","tid":467703,"uid":51343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:48:21.000Z","msg":"包庇"},{"pid":"c672e006c063fb00e13092a6d21f5a11595b6d44","tid":467703,"uid":8528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:33:15.000Z","msg":"3萬2咁少？<br />\n精神賠償呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb6a39be2df883a86e3fc51b80beb63ef578035","tid":467703,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:33:56.000Z","msg":"休班女警+1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03fb1f60be69a5c5f05d347cb851a64beea4afb","tid":467703,"uid":59504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:39:20.000Z","msg":"即係其他公司都可以拒絕向警方提供員工地址？"},{"pid":"4662b867e5b36ff9a73a33d8bf83ccfbaf09a0ac","tid":467703,"uid":27151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:39:54.000Z","msg":"警方拒絕透露女警聯絡地址<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃撚圾黑警"},{"pid":"56517a375831b589403ecfb7907edbfa7a792143","tid":467703,"uid":30058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係其他公司都可以拒絕向警方提供員工地址？</blockquote><br />\n民事同刑事既分別"},{"pid":"7cb7b6b9a8d03b01779a2bbb2e3f07f16941b855","tid":467703,"uid":156005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:16:46.000Z","msg":"TB+女黑警"},{"pid":"8f69873c57e9a0683f2bd780003a4978457712d5","tid":467703,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:18:49.000Z","msg":"26歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b432472351baf18db4e0ad6605a868c4d7c94fdb","tid":467703,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即係其他公司都可以拒絕向警方提供員工地址？</blockquote><br />\n民事同刑事既分別</blockquote><br />\n其實只要警方幫佢轉交咪得囉"},{"pid":"1aa654582dcb96262789e3b91f72695c85fe26c9","tid":467703,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:24:20.000Z","msg":"其他民事case要上court嘅話點搵被傳召一方聯絡地址？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 例如有晒對方身分姓名情況下"},{"pid":"00861fc5d28e06abc544680819c95727ce3e0558","tid":467703,"uid":3748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:11:16.000Z","msg":"2個月打兩份工先追討三萬二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1ea84789b0c75c24fe1ac37ea608035c4b442f","tid":467703,"uid":132047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2個月打兩份工先追討三萬二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你以為仕應好似連登仔咁個個30k"}]}